<sentence>定紋は丸に葛の葉。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence>（２）藤原氏支流〔寛政譜２１〕。</sentence>
<sentence>政之の系の定紋。</sentence>
<sentence>替え紋は二枚青木の葉。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
</list>
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence>青山氏　美濃国青山村に住み称号す。</sentence>
