<br type="automatic_original" />
</listItem>
<listItem>
<sentence>赤井氏　丹波国氷上郡赤井の地名を負う。</sentence>
<sentence>清和源氏頼季流〔寛政譜４、系図部３〕。</sentence>
<sentence>旗本家が出る。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
